<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Up or Down</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/intro-page.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/game-page.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.15.3/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-SZXxX4whJ79/gErwcOYf+zWLeJdY/qpuqC4cAa9rOGUstPomtqpuNWT9wdPEn2fk" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
    <div id="app-container">
        <div class="game-container">
            <div class="header-container">
                <div class="title-container">
                    <p class="sub-title">Drinking game</p>
                    <p class="title">Up👍 or Down👎</p>
                    <ul class="desc">
                        <li>🍬 게임이 시작되면 안녕봇이 1 부터 100 사이의<br/> 랜덤한 숫자를 생성합니다.</li> 
                        <li>🧃 각 플레이어는 임의의 숫자를 입력하고<br/> 제출(enter 또는 버튼 클릭)합니다.</li>
                        <li>🥤 안녕봇은 제출받은 숫자가 숨겨진 숫자보다 클 경우 <strong>Down</strong> , 작을 경우 <strong>Up</strong> 등의 힌트를 띄워줍니다.</li>
                        <li>🍺 최종적으로 숫자에 걸린 사람이 벌칙에 걸리게 됩니다.(참가자들이 원하는대로 룰을 바꾸어도 괜찮습니다)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <!-- title-container end -->
            </div>
            <!-- header-container end -->
            <div class="main-container">
                <button class="start-button">
                    Game Start
                </button>
                <button class="follow-button"
                    onclick="location.href='https://github.com/gojaebeom/up-down-app';"
                >
                    Git Hub
                </button>
            </div>
            <!-- main-container end -->
            <div class="bottom-container">
                <i class="fas fa-beer"></i>
                <span>Made by jaebeom go</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- game-container end -->
    </div>
    <!-- app-container end -->

    <script src="js/index.js"></script>
</body>
</html>